目前僅公開姓名、出生年份、學經歷、獎勵懲罰，沒有公布電話、地址。

<span class="f2">※ 編輯: billy3321 (140.109.220.235), 11/19/2015 22:28:57
</span><div class="push"><span class="hl push-tag">推 </span><span class="f3 hl push-userid">ivyclover</span><span class="f3 push-content">:</span><span class="push-ipdatetime"> 11/19 22:29
